			ConfigInfo: {
				DisplayName: 00 Configuration Info

				Headers: {
					ConfigInfo: Options with blue backgrounds have modded behavior by default. Options with gray backgrounds are disabled or use vanilla behavior by default.
					ExtraBossMaterial:
						'''
						This mod comes with 3 boss material items for bosses that don't drop materials or don't unlock materials right after their defeat. These materials wont drop unless it's assigned to a setting in this mod's configurations. The custom drops are:
						- [i:ReducedGrinding/DeerclopsFur] {$Items.DeerclopsFur.DisplayName} from [i:5109] Deerclops.
						- [i:ReducedGrinding/FishronScale] {$Items.FishronScale.DisplayName} from [i:2588] Duke Fishron.
						- [i:ReducedGrinding/EmpressDust] {$Items.EmpressDust.DisplayName} from [i:4784] Empress of Light.
						'''
